The Menu `Project=>Iconify'
...........................

If you activate this menu, the program will close the window of the
graphical user interface and appear as an icon on the Workbench. If you
want to reactivate the window, you have to doubleclick the icon. You
may also use the third gadget from the right on the upper window border.


@EndNode

@Node "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf Vorgaben zuruecksetzen" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf Vorgaben zuruecksetzen"
@Next "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf zuletzt gespeichertes"
@Prev "Der Menuepunkt Projekt=>Ikonifizieren"
@Toc "Die Menues des Programms TimeGuardian"

The Menu `Edit=>Reset to Defaults'
..................................

If you click on the gadget `Default', the default values will appear.
These are the original default settings which were shown to you after
your first startup after installation.


@EndNode

@Node "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf zuletzt gespeichertes" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf zuletzt gespeichertes"
@Next "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf vorherigen Stand"
@Prev "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf Vorgaben zuruecksetzen"
@Toc "Die Menues des Programms TimeGuardian"

The Menu `Edit=>Last Saved'
...........................

If you activate this menu, the configuration file that you saved with
the gadget `Save' will be loaded. When the file is loaded succesfully,
you may edit, use or save it in the usual way.


@EndNode

@Node "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf vorherigen Stand" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf vorherigen Stand"
@Next "Der Menuepunkt Optionen=>Piktogramme erzeugen"
@Prev "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf zuletzt gespeichertes"
@Toc "Die Menues des Programms TimeGuardian"

The Menu `Edit=>Restore'
........................

With the menu item`Restore' you may cancel changes you may have made
before. It'll work as long as you did not use one of the two gadgets
`Save' or `Use'.


@EndNode

@Node "Der Menuepunkt Optionen=>Piktogramme erzeugen" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Der Menuepunkt Optionen=>Piktogramme erzeugen"
@Next "Der Menuepunkt Voreinstellungen=>Cron Einstellungen"
@Prev "Der Menuepunkt Vorgaben=>auf vorherigen Stand"
