The Menu `Settings=>Create Icons?'
..................................

   If this menu item is checkmarked, each time you save a configuration
with the menu
`Project=>Save As', an icon for the configuration will be created.


@EndNode

@Node "Der Menuepunkt Voreinstellungen=>Cron Einstellungen" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Der Menuepunkt Voreinstellungen=>Cron Einstellungen"
@Next "Der Menuepunkt Voreinstellungen=>Log Pfad & Namen"
@Prev "Der Menuepunkt Optionen=>Piktogramme erzeugen"
