@Node "Registrierungsformular" "TimeGuardianE.guide/Registrierungsformular"

Registration Form
*****************

To print the registration form from the program `Amiga-Guide', do the
following:
   * Select the menu `Edit=>Mark', the mousepointer changes.

   * Press the left mousebutton at the beginning of the registration
     form and move the mouse to the bottom of the form. The selected
     Text will change the background colour.

   * Aktivate the menu `Edit=>Print Selected'.

     --------8<-------------------------------------8<-----------------
